ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de Terrebonne / Lachenaie (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE TERREBONNE / LACHENAIE, in Quebec, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from Terrebonne and Lachenaie to the limits of the RCM of Les Moulins including the cities of Mascouche and Terrebonne, comprising the sectors of Lachenaie and La Plaine.
